  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study presents the investigators results on patients treated for infection in the
      implemented hip prosthesis. Debridement and prosthesis retention is the method, followed by
      antibiotic treatment. The investigators present treatment results, predisposing factors and
      microbiological data.
    </textblock>
